The other more considerable towns and villages, with their population in 1831,
                    are as follow: Johnston, 5617; Pollockshaws, a burgh of barony, 4267;
                    Lochwinnoch, 2645; Barrhead and Newton Ralston, 2640; Kilbarchan, 2333;
                    Neilston, 1137; and Elderslie, 1099.
